node.text:
caelynn and i are raising money to donate to wetheprotesters and @campaignzero to take a stand against racism and police brutality. we can live in a world where the police don't kill people by limiting police interventions, improving community interactions, and ensuring accountability.

we also want to go camping with those of you who have the desire to help! by donating at the link in our bio, you and your friends are automatically entered to win a camping trip with us. screenshot your donation and dm them to us for a chance to win.

our goal is to raise $50,000. we kicked off the donations with one of our own and, if we reach our goal, i’ve agreed to let @caelynnmillerkeyes shave my head. so let’s make it happen!

node.text: Here’s the unedited and uncropped video from TdP. The post on Instagram made me chop the top and bottom and I feel like it kind of ruined the shot 😕 it was very windy and the water was very cold but I couldn’t put all that work in to get up there and NOT jump in. Thankful for my German and Italian accomplices that helped film this.

node.text:
@subway has so much new, they’re stopping at nothing to tell everyone about it…including letting me eat a delicious turkey cali fresh while plummeting toward the ground at 100mph #freshlymade #eatfreshrefresh #sponsored

disclaimer: this activity was performed under the supervision of professionals. please do not attempt to eat a @subway sandwich while skydiving.
